      <p><strong>Channel Collision Rules.</strong> Bloom & Wick (candle gifting, $110k/mo) plans holiday campaign calendar built in august. Lesson: gift segments got bundle SMS; self-purchase got Sequenzy education email. Postscript ranks #1 for SMS campaign execution; Attentive #2 enterprise; Sequenzy lifecycle email layer. Campaign marketers evaluating alternatives — index should map quarterly revenue moments before choosing software.</p>
